  "text": "Is Ra familiar with the archetypical mind of some other logos that is not the same as the one we experience. I am Ra. There are entities of Ra which have served as far wanderers to those of another logos. Enough advariance from all others that the subtleties of the archetypical mind of another logos are the most murky to the resonating mind, a body, and a spirit, the complexes of this logos.",
